      "content": "wait really?? i dont think i can go to the hospital tonight i'm home alone and it's like 2am and i dont have a car. it's probably just something i ate. if i take a really high dose of ibuprofen like 800mg it should help the inflammation and make the pain duller so i can sleep it off, right? i really dont want to deal with an ER visit if it's just gas.",
